[rl_sqs_json://<name>]
aws_access_key_id = Access key ID of the key generated to programmatically access IAM user's permissions.
aws_secret_access_key = Secret Key of the access key generated to programmatically access IAM user's permissions.
sqs_queue_name = Name of the queue accessible by the IAM user.
sqs_queue_aws_region = AWS Region identifier for the queue. NOTE: We will be searching ONLY this region for the provided queue name.